[normal]  Downhills School is 
[normal]an infamous example.   An Ofsted monitoring visit to the school, which was in special measures, judged it to be 
[normal]improving.  But the Secretary of State intervened and pronounced it was failing.  Ofsted returned within less than a term with the same lead inspector and overturned its previous judgement.  Th
[normal]e school was handed over to Harris
[normal] against the wishes of the ma
[normal]jority of parents.  The career of the head teacher was ruined.
[normal]  This debacle also brought Ofsted into disrepute.
[normal]  
[normal]S
[normal]uch tactics are unacceptable.  
